<plot>Guglielmo Marconi created this wireless station on Cape Cod in 1914, which would become the Western Hemisphere's most powerful ship to shore station. Her little-known wireless operators would play a critical role in some of the most dramatic events of the 20th century, communicating with the Hindenberg, Amelia Earhart, and Howard Hughes.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100909</url></doc>
